cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper deals with optimization of transmission mode selection and resource allocation for cellular V2X communications, which is a topic related to network optimization and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning (DRL) based decentralized algorithm, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with meeting latency and reliability requirements, which is related to control systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT).
